<i>And, of course, a</i>
<i>Ponyville fashion show.</i>

39
00:02:40,350 --> 00:02:41,860
<i>Ooooooh!</i>

40
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:45,910
This year's Ponyville Days
Festival pony of ceremonies,

41
00:02:46,170 --> 00:02:49,590
creates shimmering
