I'll say.

46
00:03:05,090 --> 00:03:07,260
I think it's going
to be magical.

47
00:03:08,110 --> 00:03:09,290
Do you really think so?

48
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:11,540
Are you kidding?
I can't wait!

49
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,580
Oh, that's such a relief.

50
